data.description: Welcome home! This is the home and location that you've been waiting for, perfect for raising your family! This 20th Century modern family home offers 4, bedrooms, 3 Baths, a 2-car attached garage and an above ground pool with a deck nestled nicely on an irregular shaped, oversized 1.62 Acre lot. The covered cement porch allows for you and your guests to get out of the elements upon arrival. The front foyer provides a large front closet and a floorplan that flows in all directions. Recessed can lighting and and a gas fireplace warm up the front room with the flip of a switch and couple nicely with the large front windows and skylights. Next, step into your new gourmet Chef's kitchen complete with a commercial grade range and double ovens. The 48" range hood compliments the stainless steel appliances and underlaid apron sink. 36" custom cabinets with 42" corner curio cabinets. The custom stone backsplash wraps around to the granite buffet counter with wine cooler opening while the oversized island floats on the custom stone flooring. With the built in breakfast bench, this is a kitchen where you can make some memories. Take a load off in your new Owner's Suite with vaulted tray ceiling and a newly upgraded Owner's bathroom with tub and standup shower. The walk-in closet is setup with custom built-ins and double storage racks make it easy to store and hang your entire wardrobe. There is new carpet in the first floor bedrooms and new LED light fixtures in all closets, halls and kitchen. The Laundry room doubles as a back entry from the pool area and a mud room with utility sink. The partially finished basement is ready to be rejuvenated and customized to your liking. Splash in the sun all summer long in your new above ground pool with attached deck and entertainment area! the 2-tier deck looks out over the 1.62 acre homesite with views of sunrise and sunset. The 2-cart attached garage has separate 100 amp subpanel and a 20 amp outlet for the 7500 watt heater with WiFi thermostat, plus a 10x12 double door shed. There is a long list of includes being riding mower, snow blower, roto tiller, weed eater, chest freezer, pool ladder, chemicals and storage bin, washer and dryer. New kitchen remodel in 2011. A/C, furnace and Aprilaire serviced by Anderson in September 2023. New water softener in February 2023. New back door, shutters, linked smoke detector system, central fan system and front storm door, plus a fresh coat of paint on the entire interior of the home. It's all here. This is your forever home and the sellers have already headed south. Call for a private showing today!
